          "severity": "transplant-ineligible newly diagnosed",
          "criteria": "older/frail, comorbidities",
          "treatment": "Dara-Rd (daratumumab, lenalidomide, dexamethasone) or VRd-lite or MPV (melphalan, prednisone, bortezomib). Continuous therapy until progression. Dose adjustments for renal impairment."
