          "severity": "relapsed/refractory",
          "criteria": "progression on or after prior therapy",
          "treatment": "Depends on prior exposure and duration of response. Options: carfilzomib, pomalidomide, daratumumab, isatuximab, selinexor, CAR-T (idecabtagene vicleucel, ciltacabtagene autoleucel), bispecific T-cell engagers (teclistamab, elranatamab)."
        }
      ]
